POST {{baseUrl}}/conflict
Content-Type: application/json

### Conflict with Body
POST {{baseUrl}}/conflict-1
Content-Type: application/json

### Conflict + Problem
POST {{baseUrl}}/conflict-2
Content-Type: application/json

